T1  - Earnings Announcements, Stock Price Adjustment, and the Existence of Option Markets
AU  - JENNINGS, ROBERT
AU  - STARKS, LAURA
Y1  - 1986/03/01
PY  - 1986
DA  - 1986/03/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1540-6261.1986.tb04494.x
